{
  "stem": "942.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And these shafts were of such size that I saw a locomotive with a whole bunch of boxcars drive right into the mountain where there were-- I think, aircraft parts were being built.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was on a detail where we were drilling another shaft.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was given an air hammer, which is quite heavy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, you know, for my age of 15, you know, I could hardly lift this darn thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to drill in this rock, like, steps going up to the top and drill it in a-- in a oval fashion, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I couldn't really handle this hammer too well, this air hammer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this work detail was run by the Todt organization, which was a civilian German organization that was building all these industrial sites for the German government.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to wear a black [INAUDIBLE] uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did not wear any guns or whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think this man had some mercy on me, and he took me off from this air hammer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he told me to take all the bits from these air drills, which used to break when you're drilling into rock-- hard rock.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I used to collect all these bits and I made, from a wire, sort of like a holder and I used to drop these bits in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had a handle on this wire cage kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I used to take about six or eight bits at a time to the smithy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I used to jump on these long conveyors that's used to take you out of the shaft and the smithy was outside in the yard.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was warm there, because, you know, there was heat.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
